<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <% content_for :title, "Admin Help - Emphases Page" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <!-- Add Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }
    .admin-page-content {
      max-width: 900px;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      padding: 30px;
      border: none;
      box-shadow: none;
      margin: 50px auto;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: left;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: left;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: left;
    }
    strong {
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <%= render 'admin/support/deployment_navbar' %>

  <div class="admin-page-content">
    <h1>Manage Emphases</h1>

    <p>This page allows you to manage emphases available within degree programs. Each emphasis entry displays a <strong>Name</strong> and offers two actions: Edit and Delete.</p>

    <h2>Existing Emphases</h2>
    <p>The <strong>Existing Emphases</strong> table lists all current emphases. Use the Edit action to modify the name of an emphasis, and the Delete action to permanently remove an entry. 
      <strong>Note:</strong> Once an emphasis is deleted, it cannot be recovered.</p>

    <h2>Create New Emphasis</h2>
    <p>To add a new emphasis, enter the name in the <strong>Emphasis Name</strong> field under <strong>Create New Emphasis</strong>. When ready, click <strong>Create Emphasis</strong>, and the new emphasis will appear in the <strong>Existing Emphases</strong> table.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Add Bootstrap JS and dependencies -->
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
